WEBVTT

00:04.288 --> 00:06.522
(cheering)

00:07.724 --> 00:09.358
D'oh!

00:09.393 --> 00:10.560
(tires screeching)

00:10.594 --> 00:11.894
(grunts)

00:11.929 --> 00:14.263
(clamoring)

00:14.298 --> 00:15.798
Okay. Next question.

00:15.833 --> 00:18.267
Yes. Will there be
another Simpsons movie?

00:18.413 --> 00:22.413
<font color="#00FF00">♪ The Simpsons 25x22 ♪</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">The Yellow Badge of Cowardge</font>
Original Air Date on May 18, 2014

00:22.438 --> 00:27.438
